61
00:06:28,010 --> 00:06:30,030
国会应该
It is time for Congress to...

62
00:06:30,030 --> 00:06:31,510
醒醒了
Wake up!

63
00:06:31,720 --> 00:06:34,120
最高法院应该
And it's time for the Supreme Court to...

64
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,550
醒醒了
Wake up!

65
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:40,600
我的目标是让美国更上一层楼
Now, my purpose is to elevate America,

66
00:06:40,910 --> 00:06:42,350
为她奋斗
fight for America,

67
00:06:42,770 --> 00:06:46,260
如果有必要的话  为她牺牲
and if it ever came to it, die for America.

68
00:06:46,670 --> 00:06:51,210
我会成为大家的父亲  母亲  领袖以及朋友
I will be father, mother, leader and friend.

69
00:06:51,210 --> 00:06:52,400
