Thank you so much.

70
00:07:00,450 --> 00:07:02,680
父亲  母亲  领袖
Father, mother, leader...

71
00:07:05,270 --> 00:07:07,490
骗子  杀手
liar, killer.

72
00:07:28,350 --> 00:07:29,660
安息吧  瑞秋
Rest in peace, Rachel.

73
00:07:43,170 --> 00:07:44,350
这是什么时候的录像
When's the footage from?

74
00:07:44,360 --> 00:07:45,890
几天前的
It's from several days ago.

75
00:07:46,110 --> 00:07:47,620
他一直待在一个小屋里
He's been staying at a cabin.

76
00:07:47,620 --> 00:07:49,830
他小时候住过的地方  待了三四周
Childhood cabin for three or four weeks.

77
00:07:49,850 --> 00:07:52,790
我们怀疑他潜藏在洛赛瑞欧斯外的山里
We suspect he's in the mountains outside Los Cerillos now.

78
00:07:53,010 --> 00:07:54,510
他找到埋她尸体的地方了吗
And did he find where he buried her?

79
00:07:54,510 --> 00:07:55,360
我们还不确定
We're still not sure.

80
00:07:55,730 --> 00:07:58,290
女士  我收到一名前探员的爆料
Ma'am, I got a tip from a former agent.

81
00:07:58,490 --> 00:08:01,590
他曾受谢泼德兄妹指使去加夫尼打探
One of the ones poking around Gaffney on behalf of the Shepherds.

82
00:08:01,880 --> 00:08:04,400
道格最近联系了赛斯·格雷森
Doug recently reached out to Seth Grayson.

83
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:06,700
我们知道他们谈了什么吗
Do we know what was discussed?

84
