I don't think it was.

728
00:48:15,480 --> 00:48:17,690
听着  我和汤姆当时在...
Look, Tom and I were working on--

729
00:48:17,690 --> 00:48:19,830
得了  我知道他在干什么
Okay, I know what he was working on.

730
00:48:22,650 --> 00:48:24,420
我花了将近一个月才找到
It took me almost a month to find it,

731
00:48:24,420 --> 00:48:26,170
但那东西在狗的项圈上
but it was on his dog's collar.

732
00:48:26,540 --> 00:48:27,240
他做的事情跟
It was the same thing

733
00:48:27,240 --> 00:48:29,920
卢卡斯和之前佐伊做的事一样
Lucas was working on and Zoe before that.

734
00:48:30,470 --> 00:48:32,480
总是遇到同样的问题
Always with the same problem,

735
00:48:32,490 --> 00:48:34,530
没有人肯相信
no one will believe it.

736
00:48:34,530 --> 00:48:37,690
-我都跟他说了  -没有任何证据
- Look, I laid it out for him-- - Without any evidence.

737
00:48:40,660 --> 00:48:41,870
难道你有证据吗
Or do you have any?

738
00:48:48,070 --> 00:48:49,070
全都是你的说辞
All there is, is your word.

739
00:48:49,070 --> 00:48:51,290
现在那还有什么价值
And what is that even worth these days?

740
00:48:53,970 --> 00:48:56,490
你到底在保护什么
I mean, what the hell are you protecting?

741
00:49:05,090 --> 00:49:07,670
我可以继续开  没关系的
I can keep driving. I don't mind.

742
00:49:09,870 --> 00:49:13,330
或者你可以帮我完成汤姆  卢卡斯
Or you can help me finish the story of Tom, Lucas,

743
00:49:13,330 --> 00:49:15,580
佐伊  你  还有...
Zoe, you and...

744
00:49:17,530 --> 00:49:18,470
也许还有我的报道
maybe me.

745
00:49:27,470 --> 00:49:28,960
我试探了你
I tested you.

746
00:49:29,500 --> 00:49:30,480
你通过了
And you passed.

747
00:49:31,000 --> 00:49:32,980
我就是这么看的  总统女士
That's basically how I see it, Madam President.

748
00:49:33,040 --> 00:49:34,490
你好无礼
You're impertinent.

749
00:49:34,730 --> 00:49:36,170
从一开始就特别明显
That was clear from the start.

750
00:49:36,170 --> 00:49:37,650
不  我有野心
No, I'm ambitious.

751
00:49:38,500 --> 00:49:40,330
我一直都很敬佩你的野心
Which is something that I've always admired,

752
00:49:40,330 --> 00:49:41,830
哪怕我在远处
from afar, about you.

753
00:49:43,470 --> 00:49:45,310
你攻击我也是出于敬佩吗
Even when you were attacking me?

754
00:49:45,570 --> 00:49:48,720
原谅我  我紧张的时候会咄咄逼人
Forgive me. I become aggressive when I'm nervous.

755
00:49:48,720 --> 00:49:49,710
老毛病了
It's always been that way.

756
00:49:50,870 --> 00:49:52,040
我们可以重新来过吗
Can we start over?

757
00:49:52,840 --> 00:49:54,530
因为我好像终于理解了你
Because I think I finally understand you

758
00:49:54,530 --> 00:49:56,400
理解了你想为这个国家做的
and what you're trying to do for this country.

759
