不管赌局猜是哪种性别
Despite what the odds-makers have decided,

765
00:50:14,160 --> 00:50:17,320
是个女孩  我就要当妈妈了
I am going to be the mother of a baby girl.

766
00:50:18,090 --> 00:50:19,930
-恭喜  -谢谢
- Congratulations. - Thank you.

767
00:50:20,170 --> 00:50:21,480
你想好给她取什么名字了吗
And have you picked out a name?

768
00:50:22,270 --> 00:50:23,090
还没有
Um, not yet.

769
