I need to see her face first.

770
00:50:29,120 --> 00:50:33,440
你最希望美国人民了解你的哪一点
What do you most wish the American people knew about you?

771
00:50:34,780 --> 00:50:35,920
出人意料的一面
Something surprising.

772
00:50:38,270 --> 00:50:40,530
我最喜欢大笑了
That I like nothing more than to laugh.

773
00:50:41,340 --> 00:50:44,130
即将成为母亲
And what does the prospect of becoming a mother,

774
00:50:44,560 --> 00:50:48,300
同时又是自由世界的领导  是什么感觉
while being the leader of the free world, feel like?

775
00:50:48,600 --> 00:50:49,950
苦中带甜
Bittersweet.

776
00:50:50,680 --> 00:50:54,450
我当然没想过会以遗孀的身份生下弗兰西斯的孩子
I didn't expect to deliver Francis' child as a widow, of course.

777
00:50:55,750 --> 00:50:59,570
但我有责任要尽  为了我尚未出世的孩子
But I have things to do for my unborn child,

778
00:50:59,570 --> 00:51:01,990
为了这个不成熟的国家
for this unformed nation.

779
00:51:02,420 --> 00:51:07,030
我想创造出进步而高效的黑尔政治遗产
I want to create a progressive and productive Hale legacy

780
00:51:07,030 --> 00:51:08,160
并影响后世
for the ages.

781
00:51:08,420 --> 00:51:09,630
说到这点
Speaking of which.

782
00:51:10,170 --> 00:51:12,100
你为什么重新用娘家姓了
Why did you return to your maiden name?

783
00:51:12,100 --> 00:51:14,060
答案就在你的问题里
Well, I think your question answered itself.

784
00:51:14,060 --> 00:51:14,960
娘家姓[少女名]
Maiden name.

785
00:51:16,240 --> 00:51:18,340
这种称呼的背后含义
The assumptions behind that expression

786
00:51:19,140 --> 00:51:22,540
让我回归了我的本名
led me back to what I can only call my name.

787
00:51:24,180 --> 00:51:25,220
黑尔总统
President Hale,

788
00:51:26,460 --> 00:51:29,320
为什么副总统空缺
why the delay in nominating a replacement

789
