迟迟不做提名
for the vice presidential vacancy?

790
00:51:31,640 --> 00:51:34,290
有两个原因  其一  是因为宪法
Two reasons. One, constitutionally,

791
00:51:34,290 --> 00:51:36,410
要求国会确认人选
Congress needs to confirm the choice

792
00:51:36,410 --> 00:51:40,370
但现在  国会乌烟瘴气
and our current Congress is dirty.

793
00:51:41,680 --> 00:51:43,870
我们得看中期选举的结果
We'll have to see what happens with the midterms.

794
00:51:44,110 --> 00:51:48,750
其二  要说我从搭档关系中学到了什么
And two, if I've learned anything from partnerships,

795
00:51:49,240 --> 00:51:53,170
你必须选一个甘愿为你挡子弹的人
you have to choose someone who'd take a bullet for you.

796
00:51:54,380 --> 00:51:56,810
还有  梅乐蒂  有件事我想澄清一下
And, Melody, I'd like to come clean on something.

797
00:51:57,110 --> 00:51:57,860
请讲
Please.

798
00:51:59,940 --> 00:52:02,070
真相是  虽然说出真相让我很痛苦
The truth is, and it pains me to say this,

799
00:52:02,080 --> 00:52:03,930
但真相是  这个国家
but the truth is, this country

800
00:52:04,170 --> 00:52:07,190
从未有机会了解真正的弗兰西斯·安德伍德
never got to know the real Francis Underwood.

801
00:52:07,190 --> 00:52:10,060
连我自己都未必真了解他
I'm not sure I ever really knew him myself.

802
00:52:12,680 --> 00:52:14,220
我知道你也看出来了
I know you saw it, too.

803
00:52:14,880 --> 00:52:18,110
他无法被看透  就跟其他骗子一样
He was impossible to know, like all con men.

804
00:52:19,130 --> 00:52:20,770
他把我们都耍了
He played us all.

805
00:52:22,860 --> 00:52:24,250
来找我啊  道格
Come and get me, Doug.

806
00:53:12,440 --> 00:53:14,020
她让我别无选择
She leaves me no choice.

